[2
Date: Thu, 19 Aug 1999 00:37:21 +0200
From: "Norman Gratz" <gratz@ibm.net>

It's true that Kosovo is within the CCHF zone. But I think that is
more likely that the "fever" is due to one of the hantaviruses which
are widespread in the area. See LeDuc et al.
--
Norman Gratz
Geneva, Switzerland
